=head2 new

=for ref

	Open or create a new HDF object.

=for usage

	Arguments:
	1 : the name of the file.
		if you want to write to it, prepend the name with
		the '+' character : "+name.hdf"
		if you want to create it, prepend the name with
		the '-' character : "-name.hdf"
